{"tid":1142384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毛澤東雕像藏冰毒　兩男女被捕","createTime":"2019-05-07T04:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T07:03:52.000Z","uid":228360,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e0e0c491a741d5ab571e5363d8b452696f503b61","tid":1142384,"uid":228360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:41:28.000Z","msg":"警方進行打擊毒品行動。昨（6日）晚約8時，大埔警區特別職務隊人員在粉嶺華明邨添明樓一單位對開，截查一名33歲袁姓本地男子，在其身上一個斜孭袋檢獲一包約重14克懷疑「冰」毒，該名男子涉藏毒被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方其後在單位內一座毛澤東雕像內，檢獲一包約重10克懷疑「冰」毒，單位內一名48歲李姓本地女子涉嫌販毒被捕。行動中檢獲的毒品市值約1.32萬元。<br />\n<br />\n兩名被捕者現正被扣留調查。警方相信行動已成功搗破一個供應毒品給上水一帶的毒品儲存中心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ma7JuBL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMa7JuBL.jpg&h=baf81cb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d774d66473aa6adbbec1ca2265ffe006d8e6498","tid":1142384,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T04:43:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66f7a8d76a55967894d237880a2f0f32bd69b9a0","tid":1142384,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:53:26.000Z","msg":"警方相信行動已成功搗破一個供應毒品給上水一帶的毒品儲存中心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2045691c9252b56c84bc11b880f0a1caaea78cec","tid":1142384,"uid":189453,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T05:59:44.000Z","msg":"用習主席雕像可能會無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"296f4f2d7d84f4ab64e0c2c0ba4e6fa397d8b3a6","tid":1142384,"uid":158411,"lik